    "body": "The correct receipts have been broken by the migration, unfortunately.\r\n\r\nPlease use this workaround to fix your receipts (will be merged into devel branch soon), PR is here: #2284\r\n\r\n```\r\nmake hack\r\n./build/bin/hack --action scanReceipts --chaindata <datadir>/erigon/chaindata --block 12600000\r\n```\r\nit checks 100k blocks after given one, and every 30s it commits the changes and prints progress like this:\r\n```\r\nINFO [07-03|13:42:59.728] Commit                                   block=12602846 fixed=583\r\nINFO [07-03|13:43:29.802] Commit                                   block=12603773 fixed=1146\r\nINFO [07-03|13:43:59.724] Commit                                   block=12604261 fixed=1508\r\nINFO [07-03|13:44:29.760] Commit                                   block=12604789 fixed=1856\r\nINFO [07-03|13:44:59.749] Commit                                   block=12605326 fixed=2160\r\nINFO [07-03|13:45:29.789] Commit                                   block=12605859 fixed=2499\r\nINFO [07-03|13:45:59.783] Commit                                   block=12606402 fixed=2826\r\n```",
